  "slug": "orange-and-almond-cake",
  "title": "Orange and almond cake",
  "subtitle": "Whole boiled orange cake with ground almonds, gluten-free",
  "excerpt": "The whole orange is boiled until completely soft, then blended skin and all into the batter. This gives the cake an intense orange flavour with no bitterness, the boiling removes the harshness from the pith. The cake is naturally gluten-free.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "The whole-boiled-citrus cake is a Sephardic Jewish method, specifically the Passover orange and almond cake documented in Claudia Roden's A Book of Jewish Food (1996), which brought the recipe into mainstream British cooking. The technique of boiling the whole fruit is widely documented across Mediterranean Jewish cookery and Passover baking.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "This is a naturally gluten-free cake made with ground almonds and two whole boiled oranges, blended skin and all into the batter. The "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "whole boiled orange",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp8796820000msv43v0q1ctz"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " gives the cake a more intense flavour than zest alone, and the boiling takes the bitterness out of the pith. Press the orange with a spoon before draining; it should offer no resistance at all. The oranges can be boiled the day before."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ingredientsList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "ingredientsGroup",
            "attrs": {
              "title": ""
            },
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "orange",
                  "unit": "each",
                  "prepNote": "unwaxed, medium",
                  "quantity": 2,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "almond-flour",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 250,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "caster-sugar",
                  "unit": "g",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 200,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "eggs",
                  "unit": "each",
                  "prepNote": "large",
                  "quantity": 4,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "baking-powder",
                  "unit": "tsp",
                  "prepNote": null,
                  "quantity": 1,
                  "isOptional": false
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "ingredient",
                "attrs": {
                  "slug": "icing-sugar",
                  "unit": "tbsp",
                  "prepNote": "for dusting",
                  "quantity": 1,
                  "isOptional": true
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Method"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Boil the oranges, about 2 hours"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Place the {{orange}} in a saucepan, cover with cold water, and bring to a boil. Simmer for 1.5 to 2 hours, keeping the oranges submerged, until completely soft when pressed."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Drain and leave to cool completely. Cut each orange open, remove any pips, then blend the flesh, skin, and all to a smooth puree."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Mix and bake"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Heat the oven to 170°C (150°C fan). Grease and line a 23 cm round tin."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Beat the {{eggs}} and {{caster-sugar}} together for 2 minutes until light. Stir in the orange puree."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Fold in {{almond-flour}} and {{baking-powder}}. Pour into the tin."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Bake for 35 to 40 minutes until set across the surface and a skewer inserted 3 cm from the edge comes out clean. The centre will be slightly denser."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Cool completely in the tin before turning out. Dust with {{icing-sugar}} to serve."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
  "glossaryTerms": [],
